snippet.title: GoddessQueen JustMe23
snippet.description:
To book a personal reading please click link for Schedulicity 
below. My readings are $75 each (10 days) & my emergency readings $100 (24 to 48 hrs)

Donations can be made at 
https://www.paypal.me/goddessqueenjustme23

Hello my name is La'Rasha & I'm Empath😯, Clairvoyant & Clairaudient 👻, Healer💫, Pyschic💜, Starseed⭐. I'm also on my own TWINFLAME & TWINRAY  journey 💙🦋!!! I decided to start my channel NOW as we all know we are in major TRANSFORMATION for GROWTH💪 for PURPOSE👐. I'm finally opening up to my gifts I have had since I was a child 🤗. I'm here to HELP & ENLIGHTEN all that is OPEN to receive 😌. 

I'm Taurus/Gemini Cusp ♉♊ 
Leo rising ♌ & Pisces moon♓ as you can see I hold all 4 ELEMENTS another one of my unique traits 🤓 I consider myself as the Magician💫. 

Mercury: Gemini
Venus: Aries
Mars: Libra
North Node: Cancer

P.S. I don't hold back my tongue...can't help it my birth chart has to much FIRE🔥 & AIR💨 in it 🤣🙅

1st video post 7/22/2018
